  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db4\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three people who took bribes to make passports illegally are caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A former employee of that office and two other persons are said to have taken money ranging from 6000 to 50,000 rupees by saying that they will prepare foreign passports under one-day and normal service for youths who come to the Kandy branch office of the Immigration Department to obtain passports. has been caught by the Kandy headquarters police.",
        "The Kandy office issues a limited number of applications for the issuance of foreign passports under the one-day service and police investigations have revealed that some of those applications have been obtained from the office by the suspects and sold for money.",
        "It has been revealed in the police investigations that the suspects have received an amount of 40,000 to 50,000 rupees for preparing a foreign travel permit under the one-day service and 6000 rupees for preparing a foreign travel permit under the normal system.",
        "Three suspects were caught by a group of youths who had come to get foreign passports while taking an advance of Rs.",
        "Among the three arrested, there is a person who is said to have worked at the immigration office for some time, a tricycle driver and a resident of Matale area, the police say."
      ],
